snippet.title: Furi - Onnamusha | Trailer [GOG]
snippet.description:
✅ Link to the game 👉  https://bit.ly/3sJaxDQ

A new fighter, new skills, new challenge! Rediscover Furi with the Onnamusha Rider: a powerful fighter that alternates between two stances: fast and agile or slower but lethal, until she's able to unleash the devastating power of the Star. A completely unique and redefining way to play Furi!
